1. *Beba* se smeši. (The baby is smiling.)
2. *Bebe* su u stanju da razumeju svoje okruženje. (Babies are able to understand their environment.)
3. *Bebi* je potrebno mnogo pažnje. (The baby needs a lot of attention.)
4. *Bebe* su obično vesele. (Babies are usually cheerful.)
5. *Bebu* treba često nahraniti. (The baby needs to be fed often.)